tracks.title: Mr. Wormwood the Great Car Dealer

metadata.description:
Matilda Wormwood is an extraordinary genius with really stupid parents. Miss Trunchbull is her terrifying headmistress who thinks all her pupils are rotten little stinkers. 
But Matilda will show these horrible grown-ups that even though shes only small, shes got some very powerful tricks up her sleeve. 
Read by Kate Winslet
metadata.author: Roald Dahl
